data.description: This three-bed, two-bath home with amazing curb appeal on a dead-end road is ready for you! The home is move in ready with beautifully refinished wood floors and new paint in the main living area. Vaulted ceilings in the living room and a semi-open floorpan to the dining and kitchen area provide a cozy space. A separate large laundry area and access to the garage are located right off the kitchen. There is an oversized primary suite with walk-in closet and separate exit to the deck. Two additional spacious bedrooms and a full bathroom are also located off the main hall. A beautiful wooded view from the back yard provides a relaxing and private space.  For a virtual tour follow the link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=llxxPxQqQFE
